==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Extense
<hw>Ex*tense"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>extensus</ets>, p. p. See <er>Extend</er>, <pos>v. t.</pos>]</ety>
<def>Outreaching; expansive; extended, superficially or
otherwise.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Men and gods are too <qex>extense</qex>;⟦br⟧
Could you slacken and condense?</q> <rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Extensibility</ent>⟦br⟧
